text: TV Bailadores is a Venezuelan community television channel. It was created in July 2004 and can be seen in the community of Bailadores in the Rivas Davila Municipality of the Mérida State of Venezuela on UHF channel 64. Carlos Andrés Pérez is the legal representative of the foundation that owns this channel.
